 i tu si stao.

634
00:37:40,420 --> 00:37:41,520
 Bog je dao tu spoznaju.

635
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:43,320
 A Bog ti želi dati novu spoznaju,

636
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,320
 veću spoznaju.

637
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,780
 Ako smo mi otvoreni,

638
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:49,120
 nemoj osvajati ono u duhovnom svijetu.

639
00:37:49,120 --> 00:37:50,220
 Došao si do nekog.

640
00:37:50,220 --> 00:37:51,520
 E, to je dosta.

641
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:53,280
 Ako ja kažem da je dosta,

642
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,720
 ja počinjem padat.

643
00:37:54,720 --> 00:37:57,700
 Zato što Bog želi dati više.

644
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:02,040
 Ono što Bog progovara,

645
00:38:02,040 --> 00:38:05,200
 kaže, ovako bi ja to rekao,

646
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:08,380
 bez vizije pogleda njegovoga,

647
00:38:08,380 --> 00:38:11,520
 ljudi su duhovno mrtvi.

648
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:16,760
 Znači, ako nemam proročki uvid

649
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:19,060
 u svoj život, u život zajednice,

650
00:38:19,060 --> 00:38:20,800
 u život kakvode sa crkve,

651
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:22,980
 mi duhovno umiremo.

652
00:38:22,980 --> 00:38:25,540
 I kaže na jednom mjestu u psalmu,

653
00:38:25,540 --> 00:38:26,660
 kaže,

654
00:38:27,120 --> 00:38:29,560
 Ako mi Bog ne progovori,

655
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:30,600
 ja umirem.

656
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:32,480
 Slobodan tumačenje.

657
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:34,480
 Znači, ako mi On ne progovori,

658
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:35,480
 ja umirem.

659
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:38,620
 I mi smo pozvani doći pred lice njegovo,

660
00:38:38,620 --> 00:38:41,340
 da nam On progovara svoje riječi.

661
00:38:41,340 --> 00:38:43,920
 I što više dolazimo,

662
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:45,800
 više prepoznajemo njegov glas.

663
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:48,260
 Jer Bog čini nove stvari u meni,

664
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:49,900
 u tebi, u životu,

665
00:38:49,900 --> 00:38:51,040
 u životu zajednice.

666
00:38:51,040 --> 00:38:53,900
 Bog želi tebe voditi tamo,

667
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:55,820
 gdje još nisi bio.

668
00:38:57,120 --> 00:39:00,680
 A mi nekad u našim okvirima,

669
00:39:00,680 --> 00:39:04,760
 možda zarobljenosti želimo poboljšati uvjete.

670
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:07,720
 Aha, živimo u tom ropstvu,

671
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:08,560
 u tom zatvoru,

672
00:39:08,560 --> 00:39:10,560
 e onda ću kupiti novi TV,

673
00:39:10,560 --> 00:39:12,940
 novi laptop,

674
00:39:12,940 --> 00:39:14,060
 da mi bude bolje,

675
00:39:14,060 --> 00:39:14,940
 da mi bude ljepše.

676
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:17,600
 Bog kaže, ne, ja te želim voditi tamo,

677
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:18,860
 gdje nisi do sada bio.

678
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,560
 I ono što meni,

679
00:39:20,560 --> 00:39:21,660
 meni je ono,

680
00:39:21,660 --> 00:39:23,160
 kako bi rekao,

681
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:25,620
 slika koja mi je došla,

682
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:27,060
 u jednom trenutku,

683
00:39:27,060 --> 00:39:28,340
 vrata zatvorena.

684
00:39:28,340 --> 00:39:31,320
 Znači, imamo vrata zatvorena,

685
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:34,000
 znači zatvorena vrata

686
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:38,020
 i u jednom trenutku će Bog otvoriti ta vrata.

687
00:39:38,020 --> 00:39:41,300
 Pitanje je za sve nas,

688
00:39:41,300 --> 00:39:43,500
 sam li ja spreman kad Bog otvori vrata,

689
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:44,620
 proći kroz ta vrata?

690
00:39:44,620 --> 00:39:46,120
 Ili nisam?

691
00:39:46,120 --> 00:39:48,740
 Jesi li spreman za to?

692
00:39:50,060 --> 00:39:54,040
 Kad gledamo dar jezika,

693
00:39:54,040 --> 00:40:00,180
 znači dar jezika te uvodi u kontemplaciju

694
00:40:00,180 --> 00:40:01,860
 i to proročko gledanje.

695
00:40:01,860 --> 00:40:03,760
 Samo treba moliti.

696
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:06,600
 Ono što sam zapisao ovdje,

697
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:08,000
 taj dar jezika,

698
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:11,080
 bila jedna anketa po našim zajednicama

699
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:15,140
 i svaki u anonimnosti treba odgovoriti na dva pitanja.

700
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:19,860
 Koliko moliš daru jezika dnevno, tjedno,

701
00:40:20,060 --> 00:40:22,600
 od suseda do suseta mjesečno.

702
00:40:22,600 --> 00:40:25,560
 I kad se napravi cijeli prosjek,

703
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:27,640
 mi smo karizmatska obnova,

704
00:40:27,640 --> 00:40:29,300
 to su zajednice u Zagrebu,

705
00:40:29,300 --> 00:40:31,960
 parnih zajednica koje su imale u anketu,

706
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:34,340
 prosjek ispada pet minuta.

707
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:37,880
 Ljudi, mi odrađujemo pet minuta,

708
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:39,340
 halalalalalala.

709
00:40:39,340 --> 00:40:42,660
 To znači da mogu moliti dva sata na zajednici,

710
00:40:42,660 --> 00:40:45,640
 halalalala, Marija, halala i šest dana ništa.

711
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,180
 Pet minuta.

712
00:40:47,180 --> 00:40:49,340
 A kaže osobna molitva,

713
00:40:50,060 --> 00:40:53,600
 znači prebivati u Božoj prisutnosti,

714
00:40:53,600 --> 00:40:56,180
 anketa je pokazala petnes minuta.

715
00:40:56,180 --> 00:40:58,580
 Ljudi moji, petnes minuta.

716
00:40:58,580 --> 00:41:01,100
 A kaže, izvoj sat vremena.

717
00:41:01,100 --> 00:41:02,760
 A mi petnest u prosjeku.

718
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:04,800
 Neko ono ima tri, četiri sata,

719
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:05,760
 a neko nema ništa.

720
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:07,680
 Pa nakraju ispadne petnes minuta.

721
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:11,680
 Za petnes minuta ti ne možeš ništa primati

722
00:41:11,680 --> 00:41:15,800
 ni ti gledati u njegovom duhu.

723
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:18,180
 Ako treba, Bog će ti dati.

724
00:41:18,180 --> 00:41:22,140
 Ali to nije životni stil koji treba, voditelj, živjeti.

725
00:41:22,140 --> 00:41:26,480
 To nije životni stil koji treba njegovati.

726
00:41:28,600 --> 00:41:31,140
 Koliko puta u molitvi ne znamo što treba moliti.

727
00:41:31,140 --> 00:41:34,900
 Koliko puta ne znamo što treba moliti.

728
00:41:34,900 --> 00:41:39,340
 Ali gospodin, kada dođeš u njegovu prisutnost,

729
00:41:39,340 --> 00:41:40,460
 čuje tvoje srce.

730
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:42,960
 Čuje srce kako ti kuca.

731
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,720
 Čuje srce kako ti govori.

732
00:41:44,720 --> 00:41:50,400
 Čuje srce kako on čuje tvoje srce kako funkcionira.

733
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:55,740
 I on nas uvodi u tu dimenziju da nas i trenira,

734
00:41:55,740 --> 00:41:59,320
 da nas obučava, da nas mijenja, da nas ozdravlja,

735
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:01,060
 da nas oslobađa.

736
00:42:01,060 --> 00:42:04,820
 On nas trenira u tom proročkom promatranju

737
00:42:04,820 --> 00:42:07,160
 ili osluškivanju što nam Bog treba dati.

738
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:09,560
 Ali jesmo li mi spremni svaki dan vježbati?

739
00:42:09,560 --> 00:42:13,260
 Ako ja svaki dan, danas, pa za godinu dana,

740
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:14,900
 dolazim u njegovu prisutnost

741
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:18,160
 i on mi progovara sigurno da će me pripremiti

742
00:42:18,160 --> 00:42:21,280
 za sve duhovne borbe, za sve duhovne situacije,

743
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:22,740
 da se pobjede sile zla,

744
00:42:22,740 --> 00:42:25,760
 da se pobjede sve ono što imamo u životu.

745
00:42:25,760 --> 00:42:28,360
 Ali ako ja ne treniram, kada dođe ta situacija,

746
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:32,180
 znači kada ulaziš u duhovnu borbu,

747
00:42:32,180 --> 00:42:34,180
 ti imaš problem, jer nisi treniran,

748
00:42:34,180 --> 00:42:39,180
 a trenira se jedan na jedan sa gospodinom.

749
00:42:39,180 --> 00:42:42,380
 Upoznaješ njegovo srce, upoznaješ što je on,

750
00:42:42,380 --> 00:42:44,640
 upoznaješ šta i kako živi,

751
00:42:44,900 --> 00:42:47,240
 i ti postaješ izvor njegovo.

752
00:42:47,240 --> 00:42:49,700
 Ti postaješ izvor svetosti,

753
00:42:49,700 --> 00:42:52,120
 ti postaješ izvor čistoće,

754
00:42:52,120 --> 00:42:54,620
 ti postaješ izvor gdje on,

755
00:42:54,620 --> 00:42:57,320
 znači to iskustvo koje susreta,

756
00:42:57,320 --> 00:43:00,420
 tebe preobražava i mijenja

757
00:43:00,420 --> 00:43:03,460
 da bi moglo biti svjetlo tamo gdje te šalje.

758
00:43:03,460 --> 00:43:06,820
 Zadnje slovo, evangelizacija.

759
00:43:06,820 --> 00:43:09,400
 Neću govoriti o metodama evangelizacije,

760
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:10,960
 nije ni bila namjera,

761
00:43:11,640 --> 00:43:15,120
 nego stav, znači sve ove pokajanje,

762
00:43:15,120 --> 00:43:16,040
 oduševljenje,

763
00:43:16,040 --> 00:43:18,320
 proročko, promatranje,

764
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:20,940
 dovodite u akciju,

765
00:43:20,940 --> 00:43:22,440
 u evangelizaciju.

766
00:43:22,440 --> 00:43:25,020
 I ono što prva riječ,

767
00:43:25,020 --> 00:43:26,980
 kada sam stao nad evangelizacijom,

768
00:43:26,980 --> 00:43:28,240
 evangelizacijom,

769
00:43:28,240 --> 00:43:31,020
 bila je rečenica za ovaj susret,

770
00:43:31,020 --> 00:43:32,000
 meni upućena,

771
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:35,300
 vjerujem da se možete svi u ovom svjedočanstvu prepoznat,

772
00:43:35,300 --> 00:43:36,220
 kaže,

773
00:43:36,220 --> 00:43:40,080
 idi tamo gdje ne osjećaš da trebaš ići.

774
00:43:40,080 --> 00:43:46,860
 Znači, idi tamo gdje ne osjećaš da trebaš ići.

775
00:43:47,420 --> 00:43:49,420
 Izlike mi radimo,

776
00:43:49,420 --> 00:43:51,980
 a ja ne osjećam da treba ići tamo.

777
00:43:51,980 --> 00:43:57,040
 Ja ne osjećam da treba ići susjedu koji je u problemima,

778
00:43:57,040 --> 00:44:01,180
 jer on neće shvatiti ako mu ja dođem.

779
00:44:01,180 --> 00:44:04,320
 Ili, kad gledam ono,

780
00:44:04,320 --> 00:44:05,700
 ne sviđa mi se to,

781
00:44:05,700 --> 00:44:07,240
 pa neću ja to raditi.

782
00:44:08,100 --> 00:44:08,740
 Ljudi moji,

783
00:44:08,740 --> 00:44:11,780
 Isus Krist je išao u Jeruzalem,

784
00:44:11,780 --> 00:44:16,160
 znajući da će ga razapeti.

785
00:44:16,160 --> 00:44:18,660
 A mogo je koristiti osjećaj,

786
00:44:18,660 --> 00:44:20,300
 aha, oni će me tamo razapeta,

787
00:44:20,300 --> 00:44:21,560
 neću ja tamo iću.

788
00:44:21,560 --> 00:44:23,320
 Joj, ne sviđa mi se to,

789
00:44:23,320 --> 00:44:24,840
 ni malo da će me razapeta.

790
00:44:24,840 --> 00:44:26,200
 Joj.

791
00:44:26,200 --> 00:44:30,460
 Introvert, da.

792
00:44:30,460 --> 00:44:33,200
 Kaže, ili ono,

793
00:44:33,200 --> 00:44:34,800
 idi siromasima,

794
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:36,580
 papa govori svima nama,

795
00:44:36,580 --> 00:44:38,020
 idite siromasima,

796
00:44:38,100 --> 00:44:40,300
 i donesite im ono što imate.

797
00:44:40,300 --> 00:44:42,120
 Prva reakcija,

798
00:44:42,120 --> 00:44:44,060
 kada ti se sjetiš da bi trebao

799
00:44:44,060 --> 00:44:45,340
 ići siromasima,

800
00:44:45,340 --> 00:44:48,400
 donijeti krštenje u duhu,

801
00:44:48,400 --> 00:44:49,160
 ili bilo što,

802
00:44:49,160 --> 00:44:50,620
 joj, ne da mi se.

803
00:44:50,620 --> 00:44:53,240
 Pa sigurno Bog mene ne zove na to.

804
00:44:53,240 --> 00:44:55,660
 Možda zove ove malo otkačenije,

805
00:44:55,660 --> 00:44:56,760
 ove na novo rođene

806
00:44:56,760 --> 00:44:59,000
 i Božju pobjedu i sl.

807
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:01,040
 Ali mene tamo sa siromašnjima

808
00:45:01,040 --> 00:45:02,800
 ne zove, ne da mi se.

809
00:45:02,800 --> 00:45:06,820
 Bog poziva da idemo onima

810
00:45:06,820 --> 00:45:08,960
 koje nitko neće.

811
00:45:08,960 --> 00:45:11,560
 I kada ja imam taj stav

812
00:45:11,560 --> 00:45:14,500
 da idem bratu i sestri u potrebi,

813
00:45:14,500 --> 00:45:16,140
 događaju se čudesa.

814
00:45:16,140 --> 00:45:18,520
 Ja vjerujem da ste vi

815
00:45:18,520 --> 00:45:20,220
 toko puto upotrebljeni

816
00:45:20,220 --> 00:45:22,160
 da vas je Bog poslao

817
00:45:22,160 --> 00:45:23,660
 onima koji nitko neće.

818
00:45:23,660 --> 00:45:26,300
 Koji su zaglibili u grijehu,

819
00:45:26,300 --> 00:45:27,880
 u svom životnom stanju,

820
00:45:27,880 --> 00:45:28,860
 staležu.

821
00:45:29,440 --> 00:45:31,540
 Bog po vama donosi pobjedu

822
00:45:31,540 --> 00:45:32,580
 u njihove živote

823
00:45:32,580 --> 00:45:34,340
 događaju se obraćenja

824
00:45:34,340 --> 00:45:35,720
 mnoga svjedočanstva.

825
00:45:35,720 --> 00:45:37,100
 Zašto?

826
00:45:37,640 --> 00:45:38,900
 Zato što se na vama,

827
00:45:38,900 --> 00:45:40,200
 na nama vidi

828
00:45:40,200 --> 00:45:42,380
 Bog koji je živ.

829
00:45:42,380 --> 00:45:44,280
 Ti si pozvana.

830
00:45:44,280 --> 00:45:45,860
 Pozvana.

831
00:45:45,860 --> 00:45:48,760
 Pozdraviti crku koja je u problemima.

832
00:45:48,760 --> 00:45:51,200
 Ti si pozvana.

833
00:45:51,200 --> 00:45:53,640
 Koja je puna svega.

834
00:45:53,640 --> 00:45:58,620
 Crkva je Božje dijelo,

835
00:45:58,620 --> 00:45:59,500
 Kristovo dijelo.

836
00:46:00,320 --> 00:46:01,360
 i pokut Krista,

837
00:46:01,360 --> 00:46:03,460
 ona daje svoj život

838
00:46:03,460 --> 00:46:05,840
 za Boga.

839
00:46:05,840 --> 00:46:08,720
 Crkva, to si ti.

840
00:46:08,720 --> 00:46:10,180
 To sam ja,

841
00:46:10,180 --> 00:46:11,060
 to je svak od nas.

842
00:46:11,060 --> 00:46:13,200
 Mi bi trebali dati svoj život

843
00:46:13,200 --> 00:46:14,260
 za Boga.

844
00:46:14,260 --> 00:46:17,760
 Ozdravljajte mlade živote.

845
00:46:17,760 --> 00:46:20,860
 Ozdravljajte brakove.

846
00:46:20,860 --> 00:46:24,580
 Ozdravljajte i oslobađajte obitelji

847
00:46:24,580 --> 00:46:25,720
 koji su u ropstvima.

848
00:46:25,720 --> 00:46:29,580
 I budimo prisutni za one

849
00:46:29,580 --> 00:46:31,840
 koji su u potrebi.

850
00:46:31,840 --> 00:46:32,720
 Amen.

